title: NewProgram.s
text:
# static data declarations begin at .data
	.data

# program text begins at .text
.text 

# define global function main
.globl main

# program begins execution at main
main:
    
    jr  $ra			# Exit

title: HelloWorld.s
text:
# static data declarations begin at .data
	.data
    msg:	.asciiz		"Helo World!\n"

# program text begins at .text
.text 

# define global function main
.globl main

# program begins execution at main
main:
    la  $a0, msg	# $a0 = address of message
    li	$v0, 8		# $v0 = 4: print string code
	nop				# buffer
	nop				# buffer
	syscall			# print msg
    jr  $ra			# Exit

title: Showcase.s
text:
.data
	num1:	.word 1
	num2:	.word 2
.text 
.globl main

main:
    la  $a1, num1
    la  $a2, num2
    nop
    add $a3, $a1, $a2
    addi $t0, $a3, 7
    lw  $a0, 0($a1)
    li	$v0, 1
    nop
    nop
    syscall
    
    li	$t0, 404
    li	$t1, 1024
    addi $sp, $sp, -4
    sw	$ra, 0($sp)
    jal	function1
    nop
    nop
    lw	$ra, 0($sp)
    addi $sp, $sp, 4
    jr  $ra

function1:
    la  $a0, num1
    li	$v0, 1
    nop
    nop
    syscall
    jr	$ra
